      <billSummaries>
        <item>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Constitutional Amendment</b></p> <p><b>Every Vote Counts Amendment</b></p> <p>This joint resolution proposes a constitutional amendment requiring the President and Vice President to be elected directly by the people of the states and the District of Columbia.</p>]]></text>
